{
  "id": "adv_event_2311_01_03",
  "title": "挑戦か無謀か",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "— The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 0.8600000024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あの、{user}さんに\n相談したいことがあるんですけど、いいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ {user}-san‚\nI have something I want to talk to you about. Is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8666666667,
      "endTime": 9.4442855517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.6509519894
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの次の対戦相手のことなんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s about TRINITYAiLE’s next opponent…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6509519894,
      "endTime": 14.7249202092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.9115869522
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それなら三人で話し合って\nトップ5には挑戦しないと決めたんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Didn’t you three discuss it and\ndecide not to challenge the top 5?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9115869522,
      "endTime": 19.9425168037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですけど……納得出来ないというか……\nなんとなく、このままじゃいけない気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true‚ but… I’m not convinced‚ or rather…\nI feel like we can’t just leave it like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1358499844,
      "endTime": 30.2758272488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.4758270581
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、自分でもどうしてそう思うのか分からなくて……\nごめんなさい、意味が分からないですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don’t understand why I feel this way…\nI’m sorry‚ you probably don’t understand what I mean.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4758270581,
      "endTime": 39.6091600735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.8158268928
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そこまで気になるならきっと何かあるんだろう\n他の二人は何も言っていないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ if you’re that concerned about it‚ there must be something.\nHaven’t the other two said anything?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8158268928,
      "endTime": 46.692947197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.8929472923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです。瑠依ちゃん達は特に気にしてなくて\n私だけが違和感を覚えてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ they haven’t. Rui-chan and Yu-chan aren’t particularly bothered‚\nbut I’m the only one who feels this way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8929472923,
      "endTime": 54.7058042526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……。すみれは他の二人より芸歴が長いから\n経験から何かを感じ取ったのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… You have a longer career in this industry than the other two‚\nso maybe you’ve picked up on something from your experience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9191374142,
      "endTime": 62.4515635807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.6582304
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "芸歴の長さ……二人には分からない、私だけの経験……\n……あっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My career… My experience… That the other two wouldn’t understand…\n…Ah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6582304,
      "endTime": 72.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.6367786407
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、思い出しました！　アイドルになる前に\n似たような経験をしたことがあったんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I remember now! Before I became an idol‚\nI had a similar experience!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6367786407,
      "endTime": 80.7125383377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "私はずっと子役をやってて自分で言うのも\nなんですけど、結構評判も良かったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was a child actor for a long time‚ and I don’t mean to brag‚\nbut I had a pretty good reputation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0325438182,
      "endTime": 88.19977757129999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.413110733
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、「このままずっと役者のお仕事を続けて\nいくんだろうな」って漠然と思ってたんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I vaguely thought‚ “I’ll probably\ncontinue working as an actor.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.413110733,
      "endTime": 96.8190286637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.0123619397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "それが、ある日突然\nお仕事がぱったりと途絶えたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But then one day‚ suddenly‚\nI stopped getting any work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0123619397,
      "endTime": 103.1340401013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは、きっかけがあってそうなったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was there a reason why that happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.3340401013,
      "endTime": 106.5524074872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.7524075349
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ。大きな失敗もなかったし、お芝居も安定感が\nあって安心して見ていられるってよく褒められました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. I didn’t make any big mistakes‚ and I was often praised for\nmy acting‚ saying it was stable and reassuring to watch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.7524075349,
      "endTime": 116.9380314668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "私も絶対にミスはしないように気をつけて\nちゃんと言われた通り演じるようにしてたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was always careful not to make any mistakes‚\nand I always tried to act exactly as I was told.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1513645332,
      "endTime": 123.9513645331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.1446976185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに急にお仕事が減って……。気が付いた時には\nもう、芸能界に私の居場所はありませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But despite that‚ the work suddenly decreased… Before I knew it‚\nI no longer had a place in the entertainment industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1446976185,
      "endTime": 136.8779400031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "……なんとなく、今のトリエルは\nあの頃の私と似てる感じがするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Somehow‚ the current TRINITYAiLE\nfeels similar to me back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1112707932,
      "endTime": 145.5822007019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.7688673496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……話を聞いた感じだと、その頃のすみれは\n無意識に安定を求めていたのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…From what I’ve heard‚ it sounds like you\nwere unconsciously seeking stability back then‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.7688673496,
      "endTime": 152.3071667194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "安定……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stability…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.5004998047,
      "endTime": 155.58215511630002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "失敗しそうな難しい挑戦を無意識に避けて\n自分に出来そうな安全な道ばかり選んでいたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were unconsciously avoiding difficult challenges that you might fail‚\nand only choosing safe paths that you felt you could handle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.7954884449,
      "endTime": 162.5033344188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.6966675042
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、失敗したくないと思うのは普通のことですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s normal to not want to fail‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.6966675042,
      "endTime": 168.2423816918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "挑戦して失敗したら、みんなに迷惑をかけて\nいろんなものを失っちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I challenge myself and fail‚ I’ll cause trouble for everyone‚\nand lose a lot of things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.4423816918,
      "endTime": 174.88940203159999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.2360667782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
