        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 350.2525245507,
      "endTime": 359.8921165307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "うちもそうや\n瑠依ちゃんとすみれちゃんの泣き顔をもう見たくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel the same way.\nI don’t want to see Rui-chan and Sumire-chan’s crying faces anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 360.09878335,
      "endTime": 365.79878344540003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr030.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 365.9987836361,
      "endTime": 368.0954746962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYで活動休止に追い込まれた時\nもうアイドルを続けられないかもしれないって思ったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we were forced to suspend our activities during I-UNITY‚\nI thought we might not be able to continue being idols anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 368.2888079961,
      "endTime": 375.4547719321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、あの時何より怖かったのは\n私のスキャンダルに優とすみれを巻き込んだことよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But what scared me the most back then\nwas that Yu and Sumire were dragged into my scandal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 375.6547717413,
      "endTime": 383.5492613157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "私のせいで二人の未来まで奪われたらって……\nそう思ったら、とても怖かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was afraid that their futures might be taken away because of me…\nThe thought of that scared me so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 383.7625944774,
      "endTime": 391.5225945154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "もうあんな思いはしたくない。私は三人でアイドルを\n続けたいの。トリエルを終わらせたくないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t want to feel that way again. I want to continue being an idol\nwith the three of us. I don’t want TRINITYAiLE to end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 391.7225944201,
      "endTime": 399.4184283892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "だから、トリエルは何があっても\n負ける訳にはいかないのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why‚ no matter what‚\nTRINITYAiLE can’t lose!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 399.6250952084,
      "endTime": 404.7980204899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 405.011353747,
      "endTime": 406.77193719539997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr031.m4a",
      "text": "……私もトリエルが大好きだよ\n三人一緒に、いつまでも笑顔でアイドルを続けたいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I love TRINITYAiLE too.\nI want to continue being idols with the three of us‚ always smiling‚ forever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 406.9586038429,
      "endTime": 417.7091710883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_03-smr032.m4a",
      "text": "でも……だからこそ……\n二人に見てほしいものがあります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… that’s why…\nI have something I want to show you two!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 417.9225042501,
      "endTime": 425.4278331913,
      "sfxList": []
